带上，所以才让姐姐带着二维码的图片。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-1468e185137e0755f3e2d653cccdb2ed_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/643402415"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIyebO5d/65thoEAMaCTEwNTI1NjA5NSD87oyuBjAAONoWQCZyCTY0MzQwMjQxNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1707438936.403156", "card_id": "Q_643546040", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 45}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2024 年，有哪些颜值实力并存的笔电新品值得期待？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-dde2c5afc1cce2032f61b27899d4fbc6_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/643546040"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyebO5d/65thoEAMaCTEwNTI4ODAyNyC5gpGuBjAAOElAJ3IJNjQzNTQ2MDQweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "40_1707438936.405920", "card_id": "Q_643528374", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 50}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "23-24 赛季 NBA 勇士 127:104 76 人，如何评价这场比赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-20904e434756a630829dba403f226281_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/643528374"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyebO5d/65thoEAMaCTEwNTI4NDA5NyChtJCuBjAAODxAKHIJNjQzNTI4Mzc0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "41_1707438936.408726", "card_id": "Q_641826562", "feed_specific": {"answer_c